                            ],
                            "activation_name": "Hat Spell"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                "text": "This larger, fancier hat grants a +2 bonus and can be activated. Each greater mage's hat has a specific 4th-rank summon spell from the arcane list woven into its fabric, typically summon animal or summon elemental . If you prepare arcane spells, you can change the spell to a different 4th-rank arcane summon spell you know when you invest it.",
